headline: GameStop earnings, November CPI: What to Watch Next Week
summary: Video game retailer and meme stock favorite GameStop (GME) will release its third quarter earnings results on Tuesday, December 10. Other notable companies publishing their latest quarterly performances include Oracle (ORCL), Adobe (ADBE), Broadcom (AVGO), Costco Wholesale (COST), and Lennar (LEN). November's Consumer Price Index (CPI) is also due out Wednesday, December 11, followed by the Producer Price Index (PPI) coming out the following day on Thursday, December 12. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination Overtime here. This post was written by Luke Carberry Mogan.
